uity capital markets mergers and acquisitions restructuring and recapitalization and uk corporate broking the company provides sales trading and capital markets platforms for cash equities electronic trading solutions equity derivatives convertibles prime services and corporate access and for fixed income products it delivers execution clearing and customizable technology solutions to trade base and ferrous metals precious metals foreign exchange and exchangetraded futures and options the company provides research and strategy to offer insights and actionable ideas on strategy and economics equity fixed income foreign exchange and commodities it provides asset management programs for convertible bonds quantitative strategies and longshort equities to private investment funds separate accounts the company also provides wealth management services such as portfolio management services executive services and family office services to highnetworth individuals family offices and others it caters to consumer and retail energy financial institutions financial sponsors healthcare industrials media and telecom public finance real estate gaming and lodging and technology sectors the company was formerly known as jefferies  company inc and changed its name to jefferies llc in march  the company was founded in  and is based in new york new york with additional offices in beijing shanghai china toronto canada and united states jefferies llc operates as a subsidiary of jefferies group llc detailed description  madison avenueth floornew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  wwwjefferiescom key executives for jefferies llc mr richard b handler chairman and chief executive officer age  mr peregrine c broadbent chief financial officer and executive vice president age  mr michael alexander chief executive officer of jefferies asia mr michael j sharp jd executive vice president general counsel and secretary age  mr howard alan rubel managing director and senior equity research analyst