t  jlc originates commercial real estate debt through a team of professionals led by mark finerman this longterm equity investment in jlc supports a  billion plus capital base directed toward new mortgage funding jlc was formed to capitalize the expansion of loancore capitals commercial mortgage origination activities loancore capital llc was formed by mark finerman in july  as a real estate asset management and origination platform loancore manages a  billion commercial real estate debt investment fund in which gic re through an affiliate had invested in  this fund focuses exclusively on the acquisition of existing commercial real estate debt senior management has originated over  billion in commercial mortgages and averages in excess of  years of experience in the commercial mortgage finance markets jlc is headquartered in greenwich ct with offices in irvine los angeles san francisco chicago and atlanta senior management jlcs senior management team is led by its chief executive officer mark finerman who is joined by other senior members of the former rbs team including perry gershon chief investment officer and chris mccormack chief operating officer mark finerman president chief executive officer mark finerman is the president of loancore capital and the ceo of jefferies loancore mr finerman founded loancore in june   mark finerman president chief executive officer mark finerman is the president of loancore capital and the ceo of jefferies loancore mr finerman founded loancore in june  he also serves as chairman of the investment committee mr finerman has  years of experience in commercial real estate finance prior to forming loancore mr finerman served as the north american head of real estate finance and securitization at rbs greenwich capital from  to  during his tenure rbs was named bank of the year by real estate finance and investment a publication of institutional investor inc prior to joining rbs mr finerman served as head of estate finance finance and se